lyTime":"2019-07-11T15:25:40.000Z","msg":"香港好似無乜要維持穩定FCF嘅現象<br />\n外國有啲都會拎哩樣為目標 例如ibm"},{"pid":"b3447bbba0893dd36a0dacafa78ab84995cfff70","tid":1306821,"uid":112161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2d4511d89e98c916aa0eb85189b0f8f02def27ac","tid":1306821,"uid":15831,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T10:57:57.000Z","msg":"多謝樓主 <br />\n我LIHKG一路有follow你架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T15:25:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c2c8b84217a0369caeda724b6d56139a00ecb07","tid":1306821,"uid":112161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2a7aa612fe235ea9fbb4099e74c3d966d4894571","tid":1306821,"uid":6240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T11:01:07.000Z","msg":"Capex 應該只計maintenance capex 定 maintenance capex + growth capex?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T15:34:33.000Z","msg":"個人認為計埋growth果個 對新經濟股 合適啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}